{"tid":2281932,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"木村拓哉IG最新近照盡顯老態　超深「路軌級」抬頭紋嚇親人","createTime":"2020-11-11T12:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T06:20:40.000Z","uid":16659,"like":34,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"a2979c5465a42d2887ac24118db8061a6aec8737","tid":2281932,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"日本男星山下智久日前與所屬公司尊尼事務所提前解約，令尊尼事務所猛將再少一員，好在快將48歲的「日劇天王」木村拓哉經歷多次風波仍為尊尼效力，絕對是忠臣中的忠臣。今日（11/11），木村在Instagram貼出一張新照片，更寫道：「我今日拍廣告！天氣又凍又乾燥，所以要注意身體狀況！」相中的他以一頭半金半黑的髮色示人，大騷型男魅力，引來不少網民讚好。不過，木村同時又曬出了頗深的抬頭紋和法令紋，非常顯老，令人感嘆歲月不饒人。"},{"pid":"a8fd13ac88073165f15d0b32acf15eb0e980d544","tid":2281932,"uid":16659,"like":77,"dislike":6,"score":71,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T12:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201111/403246102880456704396258.jpeg/o4zg9V_5xM_eR8kPN2pJ1uCeVP5Lb8MKHEGMORxBjDk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201111%2F403246102880456704396258.jpeg%2Fo4zg9V_5xM_eR8kPN2pJ1uCeVP5Lb8MKHEGMORxBjDk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=df69696b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201111/403246106022121472470125.jpeg/6R5urjhMJxE-3GrWmDfTonceFzCNROWsz-i7ks_ou5I?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201111%2F403246106022121472470125.jpeg%2F6R5urjhMJxE-3GrWmDfTonceFzCNROWsz-i7ks_ou5I%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e7a58110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201111/403246108136181760734890.jpeg/-I_OrVMPlNhSq6fPclxNUnfqIBplLinAb_jCR2_4wkc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201111%2F403246108136181760734890.jpeg%2F-I_OrVMPlNhSq6fPclxNUnfqIBplLinAb_jCR2_4wkc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=bfc89eb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef39e7304940d43bf729c05e577a6f109be92791","tid":2281932,"uid":80332,"like":441,"dislike":4,"